name: Inferno Maw Chillkeeper
text: Beneath the emerald canopy, the villagers whispered tales of the Inferno Maw Chillkeeper. A guardian of feasts, its smoldering heart scorched the night, its voracious appetite a legend. Bound by ancient charms, it stood, a fierce sentinel against the creeping frost, its fiery gaze piercing the eternal twilight.
